    <changelog>
      <entry>WMP: Added option to show map icons and, optionally, travel distances from selected map entry on the world map.</entry>
      <entry>TIS: Added option to convert palette-based TIS files into the new PVRZ-based TIS format.</entry>
      <entry>Mass Converter: Added option to automatically convert TIS files into either palette-based or PVRZ-based TIS files.</entry>
      <entry>ITM: Made icon display in ITM view tab more consistent across different game versions.</entry>
      <entry>Added option for turning on/off auto indentation in BCS script.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed a bug when repeatedly opening and closing area viewer via window close button.</entry>
      <entry>Fixed a bug in DLG resources when adding/removing action or trigger entries.</entry>
      <entry>Several smaller fixes.</entry>
    </changelog>
